00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.520
Lord, something terrible has happened.

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:55.679
The corrupted ones have appeared again.

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.479
They disrupted the Fire Festival,

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.119
and nearly killed the three Young Masters.

00:01:00.119 --> 00:01:01.479
Corrupted ones?

00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:05.120
Are they like me?

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:20.920
Minister Huo.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:23.439
How dare you barge into my chambers?

00:01:23.959 --> 00:01:24.760
Forgive me, Lord.

00:01:25.079 --> 00:01:26.480
Corrupted ones appeared at the Fire Festival.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:28.079
We urgently need you to take charge.

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:29.280
What?

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:30.319
Nonsense!

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.159
Please calm down, father.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.799
Look at what you two have done.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.680
A perfectly good Fire Festival

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:40.879
has turned into chaos, with deaths and injuries.

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:42.359
It's a complete mess.

00:01:43.599 --> 00:01:45.159
I, Nan Feng, have been brave all my life,

00:01:45.519 --> 00:01:48.400
yet my two sons are no better than useless.

00:01:48.599 --> 00:01:49.239
Eldest brother.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:50.359
Father.

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:52.200
Father.

00:01:52.439 --> 00:01:54.280
Father, please!

00:01:54.439 --> 00:01:56.000
The corrupted ones appeared out of nowhere.

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.200
Everyone is terrified.

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:59.879
I was in charge of organizing the festival.

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.840
But the city's defenses

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:03.439
have always been handled by my younger brother.

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:06.719
Who could pull this off right under my nose?

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:07.959
How could this happen?

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:10.439
This is very suspicious.

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:12.400
Someone must be plotting behind the scenes.

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:14.319
They want to frame me, father.

00:02:14.759 --> 00:02:16.000
I beg you to investigate thoroughly.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.199
In my opinion,

00:02:18.479 --> 00:02:20.879
we should start by checking the defense personnel.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:21.719
Second brother.

00:02:21.879 --> 00:02:23.400
Lord, the eldest Young Master...

00:02:23.599 --> 00:02:24.199
Zhusheng.

00:02:25.759 --> 00:02:26.560
Please calm down, father.

00:02:27.639 --> 00:02:29.039
My leg ailment has relapsed recently.

00:02:29.439 --> 00:02:31.000
I've been unwell and neglected my duties.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.879
I failed to assist my elder brother with the ceremony.

00:02:34.919 --> 00:02:36.400
I am willing to accept punishment.

00:02:38.039 --> 00:02:38.680
Reporting to my lord,

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:40.280
it was the eldest Young Master who ordered the second Young Master

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.280
not to interfere with the ceremony.

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:42.680
The second Young Master, to prevent mistakes,

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:44.199
specifically arranged guards around the area.

00:02:44.479 --> 00:02:45.960
He was even injured while saving the eldest Young Master.

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:49.439
So that's what happened.

00:02:49.639 --> 00:02:51.680
So the second brother was lying in wait all along.

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.120
Such sinister intentions.

00:02:53.159 --> 00:02:55.560
Father, you must investigate the second brother thoroughly.

00:02:56.599 --> 00:02:58.520
Eldest Young Master, how can you turn on your brother?

00:02:58.639 --> 00:02:59.639
After such a disaster,

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:00.759
you did nothing,

00:03:00.919 --> 00:03:02.319
and even used a young girl as a shield.

00:03:02.479 --> 00:03:04.039
Now you want to frame the second Young Master.

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:06.800
Zhusheng, what nonsense are you talking about?

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:08.000
Who do you think you are?

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:08.520
Is it your place to speak?

00:03:08.520 --> 00:03:09.159
Enough!

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.199
Stop arguing, this is disgraceful.

00:03:13.759 --> 00:03:16.240
If you two brothers act like this,

00:03:17.199 --> 00:03:19.520
how can Xuan City be entrusted to you?

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:23.039
I'm afraid you won't be able to protect it.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.479
Please calm down, father.

00:03:25.199 --> 00:03:26.159
It's all my fault.

00:03:26.439 --> 00:03:28.159
I will do my best to investigate.

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:29.960
Last night at the scene, we found

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.560
two suspicious outsiders.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:32.520
They are highly skilled.

00:03:32.759 --> 00:03:34.840
They might be involved in this incident.

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:35.759
Yes.

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:36.560
Yes, exactly.

00:03:36.759 --> 00:03:38.240
Those two are vicious and ruthless.

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:40.240
They must have come to assassinate me.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:53.120
Senior brother.

00:03:54.199 --> 00:03:55.479
If you don't come down soon,

00:03:55.919 --> 00:03:58.400
your dear junior brother will be crushed.

00:03:58.919 --> 00:03:59.800
Little Radish.

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:02.639
It's not that I don't want to come down,

00:04:03.479 --> 00:04:05.439
the problem is, I'm getting old.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:08.120
It's not good for me to soak in cold water.

00:04:09.319 --> 00:04:10.120
That's true.

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:11.680
You're getting old.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.319
You can't handle much trouble.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:16.079
It's really cold.

00:04:19.279 --> 00:04:20.600
Xuan City's hospitality

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.120
is truly terrible.

00:04:22.439 --> 00:04:24.360
They invited Master out of retirement,

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.800
yet they locked up his two beloved disciples

00:04:27.279 --> 00:04:30.560
in this cold and filthy water prison.

00:05:08.439 --> 00:05:09.279
Madam Sun

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:11.399
Madam Sun

00:05:14.079 --> 00:05:14.519
Sun

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.720
Why are you yelling in the middle of the night?

00:05:20.079 --> 00:05:20.839
Madam

00:05:21.199 --> 00:05:21.639
I...

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.199
I'm scared.

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:25.680
In this world,

00:05:25.839 --> 00:05:28.040
there's nowhere safer than this palace.

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:38.439
Just have some water, you'll feel better.

00:05:43.639 --> 00:05:47.240
Madam, this water is cold.

00:05:48.279 --> 00:05:49.240
Princess Yue,

00:05:49.519 --> 00:05:50.399
it's so late,

00:05:50.399 --> 00:05:51.839
and I still have to light a fire to boil water.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:53.439
That's too much trouble.

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:55.639
Just make do and drink a little.

00:06:01.879 --> 00:06:02.519
Madam

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.000
I...

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.000
What else do you want?

00:06:06.879 --> 00:06:07.720
So troublesome.

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:23.160
Princess, are you hungry?

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:24.600
Zhusheng

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:26.439
You silly girl,

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:28.399
all you care about is Zhusheng.

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.240
You don't even have room for your brother.

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:32.680
Second Brother

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.800
You're such a bother.

00:06:39.279 --> 00:06:39.959
With someone like this,

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:41.800
who has no family backing,

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.560
there's nothing to gain.

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:45.680
And still so picky.

00:06:47.959 --> 00:06:48.680
Annoying.

00:06:51.439 --> 00:06:52.360
Just trying to get you hot water.

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:58.000
Madam Sun

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:00.199
Is the water ready?

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.120
Almost, almost.

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:05.319
I heard Madam's shrill laughter just now,

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:09.439
I thought it was the sound of boiling water.

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:10.079
No.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.519
I... I didn't.

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.800
Oh my!

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:19.959
Can't even boil a pot of water.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.560
No use keeping hands like that.

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:32.160
Stop.

00:07:55.279 --> 00:07:56.279
Why do you eat like that?

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.600
This is the Princess's residence,

00:07:57.839 --> 00:07:59.240
can't it even fill your stomach?

00:08:02.439 --> 00:08:05.759
I heard there were monsters at the Fire Festival lately.

00:08:06.199 --> 00:08:07.560
I've been having nightmares every night.

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:09.240
Sometimes I sleep through the day,

00:08:09.399 --> 00:08:10.279
and miss mealtime.

00:08:10.439 --> 00:08:12.279
So there's no hot food left.

00:08:14.199 --> 00:08:15.199
These useless servants...

00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:17.199
Second Brother

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:19.360
Please don't stand up for me.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:22.319
You'll only get punished by father.

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.519
I'm not as brave and capable as you, Second Brother.

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:27.319
You worked so hard for your position.

00:08:27.399 --> 00:08:28.319
You fought for it yourself.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:30.399
Don't trouble father because of me.

00:08:30.839 --> 00:08:33.600
It'll only make him more worried now.

00:08:33.919 --> 00:08:35.720
But I can't let you suffer like this.

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:38.399
Second Brother, your injury...

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:39.519
It's nothing.

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:41.960
Just a minor wound, it doesn't matter.

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:45.000
Once I find out the cause of the corrupted ones,

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:46.519
I'll ask father for permission.

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.120
To marry you to a good husband.

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:50.080
And prepare a generous dowry for you.

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:51.240
When that time comes,

00:08:51.679 --> 00:08:53.120
I won't let you suffer at all.

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:55.039
Princess Yue

00:08:55.759 --> 00:08:56.480
The hot water is here.

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:57.480
Thank you, Zhusheng.

00:08:58.039 --> 00:08:59.360
Second Brother is still injured.

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:00.679
Take him back to the residence quickly.

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:02.039
Young Master

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.840
You insisted on seeing Princess Yue first.

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:05.120
The princess is perfectly fine.

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:06.600
You can rest assured.

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.960
That guy named Dongqing must be tired of living.

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.600
He dared to hurt you, Young Master.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:37.759
You messed with someone from the Princess's residence.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:41.440
Speak.

00:09:42.879 --> 00:09:43.559
Young Master.

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:45.120
She deserves to die.

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.360
How could she do such a thing in Yue's residence?

00:09:49.679 --> 00:09:51.080
Do you think I don't have enough problems already?

00:09:51.759 --> 00:09:52.799
There must not be a next time.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:58.200
The chaos during the Fire Festival—

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:01.360
Young Master, do you suspect Zhusheng?

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.240
If you suspect Zhusheng,

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.679
Zhusheng is willing to prove his loyalty with his life.

00:10:07.799 --> 00:10:10.679
My people wouldn't do something so foolish.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.600
The walking dead that appeared during the Fire Festival—

00:10:13.759 --> 00:10:15.799
They had a strong scent of Zushima on them.

00:10:16.679 --> 00:10:20.559
A tiny amount of this can relieve pain and reduce inflammation.

00:10:21.399 --> 00:10:22.559
But if you use even a bit more,

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:25.039
it will numb the nerves.

00:10:25.240 --> 00:10:26.600
It causes madness and hallucinations.

00:10:26.919 --> 00:10:28.960
It can even turn people into the walking dead.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:30.919
More importantly,

00:10:31.480 --> 00:10:32.720
this substance is extremely valuable.

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:35.799
One liang of the herb costs one liang of gold.

00:10:36.799 --> 00:10:38.639
Zhusheng will investigate this matter right away.

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:39.960
And bring justice to the Young Master.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:41.960
No need.

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.639
Is there any news about that girl?

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:45.919
Not yet.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.639
I'll send more people to search for her.

00:10:48.279 --> 00:10:48.840
Besides,

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:50.840
we still have a trump card in our hands.

00:10:51.399 --> 00:10:52.320
As long as she's alive,

00:10:52.879 --> 00:10:54.200
she will definitely come back for us.